Lines: We were on our way to Africa, when we received
distress call from friendly unit stuck in desert.
Distress call from allies...
We can't leave them alone, can we?
...However, this time risk
might be a little to high.
Yes... I know.
Distracting enemies in the area until Gallop can
withdraw with friendly troops.
It's not the first time we've done such things.
Everything from Far East to Europe is completly
under Federation control.
At present, it's difficult to even get through.
If you stop, you'll be encircled and defeated in no time.
But! I am sure that Brauer's Team, with our
extensive experience, can accomplish this.
That's the spirit.
Let's do it! C'mon guys!
Brauer's Squad, let's go!
Roger that!
